taskMan.resource

Class ResourcePrototype

  • java.lang.Object
    • taskMan.resource.Resource
      • taskMan.resource.ResourcePrototype
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    UserPrototype

    public class ResourcePrototype
extends Resource
    A resource prototype is an abstract resource that defines a specific type of resources. The data within this prototype will be used to define new concrete resources
    Author:
    Tim Van Den Broecke, Joran Van de Woestijne, Vincent Van Gestel and Eli Vangrieken
